The Black Dagger Brotherhood is an ongoing series of paranormal romance books by author J. R. Ward. The series focuses on a society (the "Black Dagger Brotherhood") of vampire warriors who live together and defend their race against the so-called lessers, a kind of de-souled humans threatening their kind. The first book in the series was published in 2005.Ward's Fallen Angels series is set in the same universe, and has some overlap in characters, but little overlap in storylines.